  "title": "Dify missing role check on workflow API endpoints",
  "description": "The workflow API controllers in Dify do not enforce role-based authorization. All Resource handler methods (get/post) only require login and account initialization but never check current_user.is_editor, allowing non-admin users to access, modify, run, and publish workflows via the /app/{app_id}/workflows/* endpoints despite the UI hiding these features from them.",
